# graphene-hBN-synapse

**THz Polarization-Controlled Synaptic Plasticity in Graphene / h-BN Heterostructures**

Simulation code for a biologically inspired artificial synapse based on:
- **Graphene** — tunable Dirac plasmon channel (gate-controlled conductance)
- **h-BN** — hyperbolic phonon-polariton (PhP) medium (Reststrahlen bands I & II)
- **THz polarization** — E-field angle θ selectively excites PhP modes → modulates graphene carrier density → synaptic weight update

